author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Self leveling tips over concrete…I primed the floor with Ardex P51 and allowed it to cure. Then I prepped the perimeter with Great Stuff Gaps and Cracks. The blue horseshoe shims are my height indicators, I hot glued them to the concrete. All this prep makes self leveling easier with Ardex TL 1000 🔥#selfleveling #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
